Privacy Policy for nostrTV

Effective Date: 4/26/2025

At nostrTV, we respect your privacy.
This app does not collect, store, or share any personal information from its users.

What We Collect
	•	Nothing.
nostrTV connects to public Nostr relays to display livestream events.
We do not collect user data, device identifiers, or usage analytics.

Data Usage
	•	nostrTV reads public livestream metadata (such as titles, summaries, and stream URLs) broadcast over the Nostr network.
	•	All data displayed is already publicly available.

Third Parties
	•	We do not share any user data with third parties, because we do not collect any user data.

Changes

If our privacy practices change, we will update this policy accordingly.

Contact

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at https://github/tkhumush.
